     6→ * - Counterbalanced color-word combinations
     7→ * - Accurate response collection and timing
     8→ * - Data export in BIDS-compatible format
     9→ * - Integration with PixiJS stimulus system
    10→ * - <2ms stimulus onset precision
    11→ * - Fluent API usage
    12→ */
